{
  "chapter": 42,
  "chapter_summary": "小方和阳光在密林山谷中发现三宝堂主人胡大掌柜抱头痛哭。胡大掌柜指责他们害死了他一生挚爱的柳分分，愤怒之下展翅欲发暗器。阳光机智地唱出三宝堂歌谣，以阴灵身份震慑胡大掌柜。小方趁机拔出魔眼剑刺向胡大掌柜，但胡大掌柜真正致命的伤口来自腰后，小方和阳光都意识到是卜鹰在暗中出手相助，小方兴奋呼唤卜鹰现身。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是不是人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我也是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都是人，可是你们看见有人哭得这么伤心，居然能假装没看见。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "就算我们看见了又怎么样？难道你要我们也坐下来陪你哭？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你在这里哭，跟我们有什么关系？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然有关系。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是为了你们，我才会哭的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "为了我们？你怎么会为了我们哭？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这一辈子，只喜欢过一个女人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我找了她很久，等我找到她的时候，她已经死了。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "她怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "被你们活活吁死的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "被你们吁在一棵树上，活活吁死的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道你姓方，叫做要命的小方，你想赤也赤不掉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你说的那个女人是不是柳分分？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你真的以为是我杀了她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是你是谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "如果我说不是我，你当然一定不会相信的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "燕北有个三宝堂，名气说来响当当，三宝堂里有三宝，谁见谁遭殃，两眼泪汪汪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我就是我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你怎么会知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "我怎么会不知道？我不知道谁知道？其实你也应该知道我是谁的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胡大掌柜",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我应该知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你再仔细看看我是谁？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_hu_da_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你以为阴灵是谁？你真的以为是那个瓶子？还是那个……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜鹰！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道你在这里，你为什么不出来。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜鹰！你在哪里？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 42,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    }
  ],
